<br>
So if you have 21% haste as in the FBSS, you will swing or attack 21% more than without.<br>
<br>
Anyway you slice it haste is GOD. If you can kill a mob 10-15% faster than without haste, that to me means the same as 10-15% more ac or hp's.<br>
<br>
